quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  5,32,"Kubera ibyo, twategetse bene Isiraheli ko uzica umuntu atamuhoye ko yishe undi cyangwa ko yakoze ubwononnyi ku isi, azafatwa nk’uwishe ab’isi bose. N’uzarokora ubuzima bw’umuntu, azagororerwa nk’uwarokoye ab’isi bose. Kandi rwose intumwa zacu zabazaniye ibimenyetso bigaragara, ariko abenshi muri bo nyuma yabyo bakomeje kuba abangizi ku isi"
  5,33,"Mu by’ukuri igihano cy’abarwanya Allah n’intumwa ye bakanaharanira gukora ubwononnyi ku isi; ni uko bicwa cyangwa bakabambwa, cyangwa bagacibwa amaboko n’amaguru imbusane cyangwa bakirukanwa mu gihugu. Ibyo (bihano) ni igisebo kuri bo ku isi kandi ku munsi w’imperuka bazahanishwa ibihano bihambaye"
  5,34,"Uretse ba bandi bicujije mbere y’uko mubafata (ngo bahanwe, abo muzabareke). Bityo mumenye ko Allah ari Ubabarira ibyaha, Nyirimpuhwe"
  5,35,"Yemwe abemeye! Mugandukire Allah munakore ibikorwa bituma mumwiyegereza, kandi muharanire inzira ye kugira ngo mukiranuke"
  5,36,"Mu by’ukuri ba bandi bahakanye, n’iyo baba bafite ibiri mu isi byose n’ibindi nka byo kugira ngo babyicunguze ibihano byo ku munsi w’imperuka, ntabwo bizemerwa kandi bazahanishwa ibihano bibabaza"